<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<title>练习一</title>
	<script type="text/javascript">
		
		function answer()
		{
			var x="答案是厉"
			document.getElementById("demo").innerHTML=x;
		}
	</script>
	</head>
	<body>
		<p id="demo">此字真是特别，竟然是一万多撇。（打一字）</p>
		<button onclick="answer()">查看答案</button>
	</body>
</html>

